Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 筆記本掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我會消除記憶的 請不要殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是記錄怨恨對像名字並施以詛咒的小冊子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 這是和小透的交換日記
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頁是小透寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這些大量的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶測試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比試至今遇到過的人的名字能寫出多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說記憶力真棒啊 我大概比不上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且中途開始全變成片假名了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說小透是歸國子女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那裡開始是曾看過漫畫中的人物名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪都是些怪名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱斯蒂努
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾·麗莎娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬爾·奧基斯特·瓊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·弗拉斯沃斯·維克多瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德伯奇·海肯諾比奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉斯沃·博羅尼克華科
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾·博帕魯納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧布萊恩·布科維奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷山德羅·加裡森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈爾·伊納利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德里斯·班德拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉吉歐斯·安德雷奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩魯法德爾·安德裡亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海瑟爾·波茨亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝拉斯凱斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 小透說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去她家 有東西想讓大家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去小透家還是第一次 很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在什麼地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透住的公寓很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 其實不用提前回家整理的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有見不得人的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就像是踏青竹一樣 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟老太婆似的 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透  來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著呢 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 是不整理的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 平時都整齊到過分的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌亂的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有從內側鎖著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這不像是東西亂放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看 是垃圾箱裡的東西散落出來了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 垃圾自己走出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒長手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先打掃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計不是小倫想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 亂糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這孩子把房間弄亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻貓怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上撿來的 好像被人拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 貓是有手有腳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂你在說什麼啊 小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓也能擬人化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後能變成小透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實有點能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我們也向小貓問好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變冷了啊 小透沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 吃點東西再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去家庭餐廳吧 穿商店街過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店街啊 那稍稍繞道一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想買項圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便買些貓玩具什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不會錯肯定有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:52.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成人 玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分店名是沒錯…賣的東西錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白貓配什麼顏色比較好呢 紅色？藍色？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得好認真呢 你很重視那隻貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很重視小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小透 請坐沙發那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 小倫坐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起坐不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我家的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲吧真令人猶豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你加了幾種飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次加5種美味混合飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓的名字還沒定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到好的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用點心或者飲料的名字怎樣 小透很喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有 可樂 蘋果汁 檸檬水 薑汁飲料 蜜瓜蘇打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以全部概括一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得怎樣 從今天開始你的名字就叫碳酸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這貓很老實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碳酸 項圈很相稱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛 可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃飯了嗎 現在就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 還給碳酸你買了玩具哦 吃好了一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 來聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 小倫一直被它霸佔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這時間了啊 得換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣了 毛會黏到校服上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間陪你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從早上開始一天都會很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午後降雪概率較高 出門時請多注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天氣溫驟降了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像會下雪 小倫 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是預報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶了果子露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兌雪喝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 今天早上開始就好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 你那是什麼打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽天氣預報說要下雪 這是對策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像暗殺者一樣 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定想說的不是變態？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 為什麼這麼冷還非要特地來學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是理所當然的嗎 因為我們是學生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為秋季一結束就一直放寒假到春季比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭冬天對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天你也一天到晚喊熱來著呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種天還要下雪 我沒有活下去的自信呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可憂鬱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪能做好多開心的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆雪人啊 做雪屋啊 還可以打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以凪也來祈願今天能下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才沒聽我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.68,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一節課
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.67,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.33,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:07.08,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四節課
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會下雪…絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒放棄對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經放棄一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部放棄掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.17,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真是瞬息萬變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 午飯 午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去吃雪 吃你的便當呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子會積起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勢頭很好啊 要是積得很厚了 我想這麼做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋到深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像漫畫裡一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這跳下去的話能不能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從屋頂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積起來了呢 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也撲到雪裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要突然這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然幹什麼啊 很危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優子擺的pose好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪蠻暖和的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很冷的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 讓凪變得暖和起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢 小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為凪做個雪屋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個很暖和呢 我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒 凪 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似很狹窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 暖和嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外面暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然攻擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面玩成那樣 居然沒有感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感冒了T_T 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒到38度了 小透
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像感冒了 小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:38.28,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像也感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們 努力清除積雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.65,0:23:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年冬天幹了什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:24:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了準備中考柚多谷一直在教美穗功課
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「A Channel」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.71,0:24:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家考試複習加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當現在是幾月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:24.76,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣預報是下雪的標記 我雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:31.99,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天冷什麼的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:37.36,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.77,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望著的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:48.85,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的話就太幸運了 一時興起堆起雪人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:53.21,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:58.47,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情模仿潛水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:03.71,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要雪天 開心的雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:08.44,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多下些堆積起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.00,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.64,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直下下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.92,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:22.76,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多下些堆積起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.32,CQ-C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心的雪天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:08.88,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}茜に並ぶ背高影法師　楽しい一日の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:17.46,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}尽きないお喋り　まだまだあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:24.89,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}そろそろお家に帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:32.05,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}じゃあね明日ね　メールするから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:39.56,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}今日のページに皆お揃いの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:46.58,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}じゃあね明日ね　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:55.35,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}今日も一緒に入れてよかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:23:02.47,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}るるる～　風と心ハミングする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:09.09,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}次の角で振り向きながらバイバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:22:08.88,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}長長的茜色影子排著隊 是開心一天的結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:17.46,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}雖然還有很多說不完的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:24.89,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}可惜是時候要回家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:32.05,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}byebye明天見 我會短信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:39.56,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}今天的一頁也湊齊了大家的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:46.58,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}byebye明天見 一直以來謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:55.35,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}今天也能加入進來真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:23:02.47,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}{\fad(200,200)}嚕嚕嚕～ 與風兒一起在心中哼著歌
